0:08:36.26,000 --> 0:08:39,000
And we say that word with such contempt.

211
0:08:39.26,000 --> 0:08:41,000
But it's that contempt

212
0:08:41.26,000 --> 0:08:44,000
that keeps this thing that we own

213
0:08:44.26,000 --> 0:08:46,000
and we pay for

214
0:08:46.26,000 --> 0:08:49,000
as something that's working against us, this other thing,

215
0:08:49.26,000 --> 0:08:52,000
and then we're disempowering ourselves.

216
0:08:52.26,000 --> 0:08:55,000
People seem to think politics is sexy.

217
0:08:55.26,000 --> 0:08:58,000
If we want this institution to work for us,

218
0:08:58.26,000 --> 0:09:01,000
